Local Test: Run mvn spring-boot:run and check localhost:8080/api/notes.

Docker Build: Run docker build -t notes-app ..

Docker Run: Run docker run -p 8080:8080 notes-app.

K8s Deploy: * Ensure kubectl is connected to a cluster (like Minikube).

Run kubectl apply -f k8s/deployment.yaml.

CI/CD: Push your code to GitHub. Add your DockerHub credentials to GitHub Secrets. The pipeline will automatically test, build, and push the image.
